//Posttraumatic

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 04 - Bones of Shoulder MRI
When I select the radio button 'Finding'
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select 'Posttraumatic' from the Finding dropdown
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Hill-Sachs-Lesion' radio button is enabled
And 'Reverse Hill-Sachs-Lesion' radio button is enabled

And 'Serial number' input field is enabled
And 'Image number' input field is enabled
And 'Import reference image' image uploader field is enabled

When I select 'Hill-Sachs-Lesion' radio button
Then 'Impression postero-superior' checkbox is enabled
When I select 'Impression postero-superior' checkbox
Then 'Angle circumference' inout field is enabled

When I select 'Reverse Hill-Sachs-Lesion' radio button
Then 'Impression antero-superior' checkbox is enabled
When I select 'Impression antero-superior' checkbox
Then 'Angle circumference' inout field is enabled
